data.description: COME FALL IN LOVE WITH THIS HOME!! Great floor Plan!! Don't miss this spacious floor plan with 2 large living areas perfect for entertaining; kitchen opens to family room, gas fireplace, and built in bookcases. Main suite  comes with 2 walk-in closets. 4th bed is great for guest, in-law, or flex room. Fresh paint throughout. New HW Tank, Newer Roof... Parking Galore, Newer tile floor throughout, and updated bathrooms. Neighborhood pool, tennis courts and park! Don't miss this one! Book your showing today!
